<i>♪ Just in case</i>

08:16.321 --> 08:18.802
What the fuck
are you doing here?

08:18.802 --> 08:22.589
I don't want to waste your time,
so I'm gonna make this simple.

08:22.589 --> 08:24.155
You take no action
against Che

08:24.155 --> 08:26.331
that would endanger Malcolm
at the United Nations.

08:26.331 --> 08:27.985
He's my brother.

08:27.985 --> 08:30.074
He's my homeland.

08:30.074 --> 08:31.772
You understand?

08:33.643 --> 08:36.167
You want to protect
your friend?

08:36.167 --> 08:38.866
Advise him not to show up.

08:41.346 --> 08:44.219
Excuse me. I got a date.

09:07.982 --> 09:11.202
You know what my father
always said?

09:11.202 --> 09:13.248
The IRS is your friend.

09:14.379 --> 09:16.207
- Friend?
- Mm-hmm.

09:16.207 --> 09:18.862
I'd like to go down
to Washington

09:18.862 --> 09:21.735
and personally blow up
their fucking headquarters.

09:21.735 --> 09:24.346
<i>♪ Pretty baby</i>

09:24.346 --> 09:27.262
