four cents a gallon for the IRS

09:46.760 --> 09:49.284
and you're paying them.
Why?

09:49.284 --> 09:51.982
'Cause it's
four fucking cents.

09:51.982 --> 09:54.855
Shit like that's what got
Al Capone thrown in jail.

09:54.855 --> 09:56.813
- I got a better idea.
- Oh, yeah?

09:56.813 --> 09:58.423
Keep the taxes for a year,

09:58.423 --> 10:01.165
then go out of business
and start new companies.

10:01.165 --> 10:03.646
<i>♪ You need me by your side</i>

10:03.646 --> 10:05.648
For the gas stations?

10:05.648 --> 10:08.259
Exactly. Then legally,
they can't collect.

10:08.259 --> 10:09.913
You get to keep
the four cents,

10:09.913 --> 10:13.830
which comes to about...
$1.8 million a year.

10:13.830 --> 10:15.745
<i>♪ Honey, you can run
to the west ♪</i>

10:17.834 --> 10:22.665
Oh, that big, beautiful
brain of yours!

10:22.665 --> 10:23.884
Mwah!

10:23.884 --> 10:25.929
